title: Big Brother USA 9 Live Feeds - 03-07-08
description:
Big Brother USA Live Feeds - 03/07/08 - xx2000xx

For youtube vids + exclusive content go to - http://bbcouchpotatoes.blogspot.com/

From a game perspective this was by far the craziest day. Ryan flipped 3 different times and is all over the place.

Part 1 - 6 min
Right after POV. Chelsia won. Ryan confirms their plan and he&#039;s going to backdoor Matt.

Part 2 - 7 min
Chelsia comes up to the HOH room. He tells Chelsia that the plan is still in effect and Matt will leave Wed.

Part 3 - 8 min
Matt knows something might go down and freaks out. He goes to the HOH room and Ryan really doesn&#039;t say anything. After this he went outside and sat alone in the hammock an hour.

Part 4 - 33 min
Sheila has a true heart to heart with Adam. She breaks down and tells him that they&#039;re basically screwed if they put up Matt because they&#039;re next. - Adam talks to Ryan about putting up Matt, Ryan doesn&#039;t deny it - Sheila has the game figured out and tells Nat everything.

Part 5 - 42 min
Sheila pulls the move of the season. She flips Ryan in a span of 12 min. Excellent stuff here - A new alliance is formed. Matt/Nat/Sheila/Adam/Ryan. Shades of bb6 here. They want to take out the ring leader in Josh. - Josh reads his letter that he won at POV from his Mom - The other side of the house talks smack about the new alliance and how Matt is going this week while making fun of him.

Part 6 - 33 min
Ryan comes up with a plan out of nowhere to take out James. We have our first big pow wow of the season and Matt/Ryan/Adam want to take out James this week. I think Ryan is dead set on this one too.

Part 7 - 39 min
New alliance members Nat/Adam talk about the game - Adam tells a story about almost dying - More of the new alliance talk - Sheila/Nat talk about the crazy day - Nat talks to Ryan alone in the HOH room.
